title: Hellboy - Wake The Devil (Digital-Enhanced) (Falaaee)
description: Hellboy's back in action with the Bureau for Paranormal Research and Defense, in a full-scale mission to hunt the legendary nobleman vampire, Vladimir Giurescu, who is woken by the same newly defrosted Nazis seen in Hellboy: Seed of Destruction. The Bureau is walking into the biggest disaster in its fifty-year history! Also in this five-issue series, Mike Mignola and Dark Horse are proud to introduce the newest mysterymen on the block, Gary Gianni's (Shadow: Hell's Heatwave) MonsterMen in "Silent as the Grave"!
